Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:37.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}那些家伙见了就是修罗场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:38.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}修罗场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}恳请切莫趟这浑水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:50.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}之所以成为修罗场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}当然是因为俩家伙见了面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:56.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}找来了各种不请自来的问题
